title: America - Highway - 30 Years of America (3 Discs) [2000]
description:
Highway: 30 Years Of America is the third principal major label compilation album by American folk rock duo America, released in 2000. The collection represented the first boxed set release of America's material which spans America?s entire hit-packed career, featuring singles, album cuts, and previously unreleased tracks.

Original Release Year: 2000
Genre: Rock/Pop
